'''Robbie Magasiva''' ([[1972]]) is a New Zealand actor, part of the comedy group [[wikipedia:Naked Samoans|Naked Samoans]]. He played [[Mauhúr]] in ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]''.
==Quotes==
{{quote|That was only 30 seconds of nastiness. I want two hours' worth of nastiness on the big screen.|Robbie Magasiva on playing Mauhúr, [http://www.listener.co.nz/issue/3442/features/5970/robbie_magasiva.html ''New Zealand Listener'' interview]}}
